text: Area codes 407 and 689 are area codes for Florida. Area code 407 was created in 1988 when it was split from area code 305. It covers Orlando, Apopka, Winter Park, Altamonte Springs, Kissimmee, and Sanford. It was overlaid by 321 in 1999 and 689 in 2019. Category:Florida 407 and 689
title: Area codes 407 and 689
